ry of Active\nGalactic Nuclei at the per cent level will be possible, making for a real\nbreakthrough in high energy astrophysics.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 16 Nov 2006 08:47:54 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 20 Nov 2006 08:38:33 GMT"}],"update_date":"2008-11-26"}
